The '''Intergalactic Federation of Musicians (IFM)''' was a trade guild organization whose function was to protect and promote the business interests of singers, songwriters and performance artists across the galaxy. The popular [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]-based [[Jizz/Legends|jizz]] band known as the [[Figrin D'an and the Modal Nodes/Legends|Figrin D'an and the Modal Nodes]] were members of the Intergalactic Federation of Musicians.

